import { Modal, ModalBody, ModalHeader , ModalFooter,Button,FormGroup,Input,Label,Form } from "reactstrap";
const AddStaffs = ({isOpen}) => {
  return (
    <>
       <form >
        <Modal isOpen={isOpen}>
          <ModalHeader >Thêm nhân viên
          </ModalHeader>
          <ModalBody>
          <Form className="form">
          <FormGroup className="row">
            <Label for="name" className="col-3">Tên</Label>
            <Input
              className="col-8"
              type="name"
              name="name"
              id="name"
            />
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup className="row">
            <Label for="name" className="col-3 mt-2">Ngày Sinh </Label>
            <Input
              className="col-8"
              type="date"
              name="doB"
              id="doB"
            />
          </FormGroup>
          <FormGroup className="row">
            <Label for="name" className="col-3 mt-2">Ngày vào công t </Label>
            <Input
              className="col-8"
              type="date"
              name="doB"
              id="doB"
            />
          </FormGroup>
          </Form>
          </ModalBody>
          <ModalFooter className="modal-footer border-0">
            <Button className="btn_secondary modal-btn" >
            </Button>{" "}
              
            <input
              className="btn btn_primary modal-btn"
              type="submit"
              value='Thêm'
            />
          </ModalFooter>
        </Modal>
      </form>
    </>
  );
};
export default AddStaffs;
